Package assignmentevaluator.evaluationHelpers.executors

Class TestExecutor

java.lang.Object
assignmentevaluator.evaluationHelpers.executors.TestExecutor
public abstract class TestExecutor extends Object
Abstract base class for executing tests on a student's assignment. Subclasses implement specific test execution logic for different test types.
